{"id":"eb298113-ff11-41d1-9ea1-f3e98a5fa113","name":"Your Imaginary Friend Never Really Went Away","description":"<p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/M4WonGilsM7AZL1ySrcG5.webp\"></p><p><strong>(AnyPOV)</strong> You had an Imaginary Friend as a child. The problem is, even as you grew up, she never went away.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XY-T4q3JwLZzQPjCYcYzP.webp\"><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>▔▔▔▔</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(96, 95, 200);\"><strong>Darling!<br>It's me, your Violetta!</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br><br>Oh, Darling! We did it! This is it!<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(96, 95, 200);\"><strong>We are nearing the end!</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br><br>Soon enough, <strong>these shadows will dissipate and we'll finally be together</strong>!<br><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(96, 95, 200);\"><strong>We just need one more story. One more, that's all it takes!</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br>So stay by my side as I tell you...<br><strong>The last story.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_7qSFUn_XGe1fblRkMRit.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">▔▔▔▔<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>This is it, my love.</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br>My city. Your city. <strong>Mind Harbor!</strong><br><br>And for the sole purpose of this story — </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>this is where you grew up.</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br><br>Where you learned how to ride a bike. Where you graduated. </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>Where you lived your whole life.</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br><br>To many, <strong>Mind Harbor is a strange anomaly</strong>. A failed tourist trap. A lonely little place in the desert.<br><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>But you were never alone.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4TASQZRjgakSkmDQXdrCv.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">▔▔▔▔<br><strong>Many children have imaginary friends while growing up</strong>. I know I had a few!<br><br>You were no different. </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>And her name was Zozo.</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><br><br><strong>But imaginary friends aren't supposed to last forever</strong>. Well, it seems like Zozo never got the memo. </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>Because she never left you</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.<br><br>Through first kisses, first loves, graduation, jobs... she was always there. </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(172, 141, 66);\"><strong>Always teasing. Always speaking her mind.</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"hEHLPU1N7GNjX_tvctrQA.webp","creator":"AlissaOne","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🔦 Horror","😂 Comedy"],"chats":13010,"messages":159561,"created_at":"2026-05-27T11:16:29.976172+00:00"}